			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>An alchemist of unparalleled talents, so much<br>so that she was successfully able to create the<br>legendary omega key. After the death of her<br>parents, she was raised by a faerie. She yearns<br>to be free, but the world is greedy for her talents.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/775392a8a09a554df496b2a54960c3e62.png"></span>
