			<dd>
				<div>
					Deals light damage to multiple targets, and<br>inflicts flashburn. If the user has one or more<br>alchemic cartridges, it will deal light damage<br>to enemies in a line, inflict flashburn,<br>and consume one alchemic cartridge.
				</div>
			</dd>
	<dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/20cad8e4fa011f9a61e0e16c16dc42ba2.png"></span>
				<span>Alchemic Enhancement</span>
			</dt>
			<dd>
				<div>
					Unlocking this skill grants the user<br>an alchemy gauge. If the user does not<br>have any alchemic cartridges,<br>the alchemy gauge will fill when<br>standard attacks, dodge attacks, or<br>force strikes connect with enemies.<br>The alchemy gauge charges faster when<br>the combo count is 30 or higher.<br><br>This skill can only be used when the user's<br>alchemy gauge has one or more charges.<br><br>Grants the user an alchemic cartridge<br>for each charge of the alchemy gauge.<br>These cartridges last for 20 seconds.<br>Alchemic cartridges grant the user<br>a unique force strike that consumes<br>all remaining alchemic cartridges.<br>The number of hits this unique force<br>strike deals is based on the number<br>of alchemic cartridges consumed.<br><br>If the user has one or more alchemic<br>cartridges, this skill will instead deal<br>light damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and consume one alchemic cartridge.
				</div>
			</dd>
