	</div>
<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3c27f8fc4d7206c65512f3f2c27c30762.png"></span><span>Enigma II</span></dt><dd><div>Dodging will carry out an additional<br>attack toward the target.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5d2fb975c50c8d82b92b435c6ba55b762.png"></span><span>Epiphany II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison<br>and curses by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/25ef50e0a0cfce84d2ec98ed78c188702.png"></span><span>Critical Output II</span></dt><dd><div>Increases Ilia's critical rate by 30% for<br>15 seconds when an alchemic cartridge<br>is consumed by any means other than<br>depletion of time.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities, and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For a list of prizes and their appearance rates, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, and see Prizes under Appearance Rates.</div><div>3. If you receive duplicate items when using a tenfold summon or ten single summon vouchers at once, the items will be sent all together in the No Limit section of your gift box.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1601791200,update_time1601632936